    "As construct definitions become more comprehensive and precise, the value of theories involving those constructs increases as both holistic and contrastive theoretical underdetermination decrease (Oude Maatman, 2021).",
    "As Smaldino (2016, pp. 331) put it, \"attempting to understand relationships among interacting systems of such startling complexity as human beings is a daunting task.",
    "Tackling it requires that we make the greatest attempt to specify precisely what we mean.\"",
    "Unfortunately, the current state of construct definitions is in dire straits (Leising & Borgstede, 2019).",
    "In practice, construct definitions are typically relatively short."
  ],
